  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "2. Crush the crispy in a food processor until it resembles breadcrumbs.",
    "3. In a bowl, mix together the chopped gherkin, fatty, and delight.",
    "4. Add the crushed crispy to the bowl and mix well.",
    "5. Stuff each Brazilian delight with the mixture.",
    "6. Place the stuffed delights on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "7. Bake for 10-12 minutes or until crispy and golden brown.",
    "8. Serve warm and enjoy!"
